{"tid":258673,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"咁好景？港IT安全工程師年薪150萬 (17:43)","createTime":"2017-05-26T10:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T02:45:23.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3c885312246edd43c5b5fb01e029ce41b3bb70","tid":258673,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170526/img/20170526174333fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170526%2Fimg%2F20170526174333fi_p1.jpg&h=2f5ad67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=TGTqHqhYQ5HuTztOJEdLc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=327586f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】人力資源顧問公司Robert Half發表《2017年薪酬指南》，透露香港十大加薪幅度最高的IT職位，而香港科技專才的今年薪酬可望平均增加4.3%。由於網絡保安人才奇缺下，本港資訊科技的安全工程師或風險管理主管年薪高達150萬元，按年增加14%，無論年薪以至今年加薪幅度，都遠高於銀行界別大多管理層平均年薪60萬元，以及加薪幅度3%至4%。<br />\n<br />\n近日席捲全球的病毒攻擊Wannacry引起全球對網絡保安的關注。Robert Half報告指，對於能勝任熱門職位的IT頂尖人才，由於他們了解自己的市場價值，因此有能力爭取更佳待遇。而報告列出今年香港十個IT職位，其中加薪幅度最高的是雲運算工程師，今年的加幅達16.2%，年薪最高的職位是資訊科技安全工程師或資訊科技風險管理主管，年薪達150萬元。另一新興的職位敏捷專家(Scrum Master)，在敏捷開發環境帶領DevOps團隊導入Scrum模式。<br />\n<br />\n安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍表示，目前IT行業面對嚴重的人力短缺問題，例如電腦保安的工作，只有少於5人應徵，有時甚至沒有。她又指，IT職位種類多，而且也要看公司類型，所以平均年薪難一概而論，但現時不少行業都需要依賴科技，所以一些IT職位比銀行業管理層平均年薪60萬元為高。而且2017年IT職位的平均加薪幅度約5%，相對銀行業的3至4%，IT職位亦更高。事實上，Robert Half報告羅列的本港10大高薪IT職位，今年加薪幅度最高達16.2%。<br />\n<br />\n她續指，現時最受年輕人歡迎的IT工作屬手機程式開發，因爲這個行業比較新，而且有趣，所以能吸引他們入行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170526/20170526174333fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170526%2F20170526174333fi.html&d=TGTqHqhYQ5HuTztOJEdLc7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=84197993\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170526/20170526174333fi.html</a><br />\n<br />\n//腦魔入嚟講2句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89035a4cb64c853b4fb2d9d654f126092abe1d8c","tid":258673,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"呢D高級IT，唔係做清潔的IT。兩個層次嚟。正係英文都差十幾級。"},{"pid":"77792673f02b548c6c4ee336ae3dbcaa584e63c6","tid":258673,"uid":53648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd5203a3a430106502f31706daebe9f9fc04d407","tid":258673,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銀行界別大多管理層平均年薪60萬元</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間銀行咁CHEAP&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2649847e45af836e13a3e0c12574e26fef1ac579","tid":258673,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"梁國雄去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2382bd8e4d89241d8e3e14a9f47cc196f0ed2eee","tid":258673,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"梁國雄議員"},{"pid":"7879992747161980dc2bce1d5acec194b3fd49ae","tid":258673,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"呢班唔係叫人reboot果人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76218acdb84a3646fcaa470bb624e853d3cafc46","tid":258673,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z4LiIof.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ4LiIof.png&h=35444764&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba2e6731ddd67c96fcfdacb006bc15a433d76867","tid":258673,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/ad/Z1oV1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20110325121205\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h